---
title: Basa in Creamy Cajun Sauce with Spiced Chips and Tomato Salad
description: Punchy and smoky with a spicy kick, Cajun spice mix contains ingredients such as chilli powder, ground cumin, oregano and thyme. The spiced Cajun sauce pairs perfectly with basa, a delicate white fish that's great for soaking up flavour.
